{"tid":2293582,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【PS5】英國最大銷售商：「PS5太大部影響送貨」","createTime":"2020-11-20T10:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T11:27:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a45a1218d7be7cbf3ffc23a50b2cec5259a4295","tid":2293582,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:37:43.000Z","msg":"PS5比起PS4當然有好多進步，但我夠膽講PS5得到最多嘅評價，一定唔係啲畫有幾靚、Load得有幾快，而係「部機咁大部嘅？」作為歷年黎最大部嘅遊戲主機，PS5唔單止為大家帶來擺放 (及偷運) 嘅問題，英國最大嘅遊戲銷售商「Game」更加將開賣首日嘅物流問題歸咎於PS5嘅大小之上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/11/20/9d2007d286ac9288176ae3eefa7e4b3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F11%2F20%2F9d2007d286ac9288176ae3eefa7e4b3c.jpg&h=9cd8e5c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Game」日前向預訂咗PS5嘅客戶發出嘅電郵，指因為「PS5於英國市場嘅貨量以及產品嘅大小，令英國出現大範圍的物流問題」，然後就話，負責送貨嘅其中一間物流供應商「Yodel」指，因為單量超出上限，所以訂咗PS5嘅玩家或者未能於19號開售當日收到機，而可能要等到星期五。簡單啲黎講，就因為Game將「收唔到機」呢個鑊卸咗畀Yodel。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.menclub.hk/data/attachment/object_pic/2020/11/20/637bf4fd9aebc4bcb676f725524f78f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.menclub.hk%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fobject_pic%2F2020%2F11%2F20%2F637bf4fd9aebc4bcb676f725524f78f7.jpg&h=e54ced61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有趣嘅係，Yodel隨後向BBC發出回應，話「我哋一直穩定地完成Game畀我哋嘅運送訂單，對於Yodel個名被錯誤地用作解釋客人收唔到機感到非常失望」，亦即係話「唔關我事唔好賴我！」另一邊廂，由於英國目前處於封城狀態，玩家們只能上網購買PS5，所以Game、Amazon等多個網站嘅PS5頁面都係長期Load唔到。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：The Verge"},{"pid":"0cfbc60aea0664e8cff3a9a53953a51ff6062919","tid":2293582,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"無錢買PS5了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1a3329fa326e6db528660f81dc7c654d5b9d58","tid":2293582,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cfbc60aea0664e8cff3a9a53953a51ff6062919","tid":2293582,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"無錢買PS5了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"送多幾個外賣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d79c7b3caaa6fd5ae581c389183aead079796674","tid":2293582,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1a3329fa326e6db528660f81dc7c654d5b9d58","tid":2293582,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cfbc60aea0664e8cff3a9a53953a51ff6062919","tid":2293582,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"無錢買PS5了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"送多幾個外賣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"遠遠不夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ba719d399e0579752af58650c7d19ca89f4537e","tid":2293582,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"英國研究指：PS5或增加大屋、大貨櫃車、大型倉庫及大鋪嘅需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b2c967e3c29972b1c06c24f80b9bd2165421e90","tid":2293582,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T11:27:39.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}